  <brief_title>The Effect of Cipralex on Quality of Life, Adrenal Activity Glucose Metabolism, Physical and Mental Health in PCOS</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Cipralex in Polycystic Ovary Syndrome</official_title>
